{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PvEDGdaDG4eNWTdHjAEKhr","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've retrieved all six files. Here's a summary of the E2E test infrastructure:\n\n---\n\n## **E2E Test Infrastructure Summary**\n\n### **1. Platform App Test Scripts** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/package.json`)\n\nThree test commands are defined:\n- `test:visual` — Playwright visual snapshot tests (base config)\n- `test:visual:update` — Update visual snapshots\n- `test:real` — Real integration tests (`playwright.real.config.ts`)\n- `test:e2e:local` — Local E2E tests with localnet validator (`playwright.local.config.ts`)\n\n---\n\n### **2. Bootstrap Script** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/scripts/localnet-bootstrap.sh`)\n\n**Purpose**: Start a fresh `solana-test-validator` with coinflip + platform programs preloaded.\n\n**Key Steps**:\n1. Preflight checks for compiled `.so` files and keypairs\n2. Verifies `io_uring` syscall availability (Solana 3.x requirement)\n3. Kills any existing validator on port 8899\n4. Cleans ledger for fresh state\n5. Starts validator with:\n   - Programs: `coinflip` (ID: `BdHFeqmkYe7znXV1Avk3zz496Pjo8QhEDN4MKPUTAWwx`)\n   - Programs: `platform` (ID: `85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA`)\n   - Mock Orao VRF accounts (preloaded for deterministic tests)\n6. Waits for RPC health check (30s timeout)\n7. Writes validator PID to `.localnet.pid`\n\n**Outputs**: `.localnet.pid`, `.localnet-ledger/`, `.localnet-validator.log`\n\n---\n\n### **3. Teardown Script** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/scripts/localnet-teardown.sh`)\n\n**Purpose**: Stop validator and clean temp files.\n\n**Key Steps**:\n1. Reads PID from `.localnet.pid`\n2. Gracefully stops validator (5s wait, then force kill)\n3. Kills stray processes on port 8899\n4. Removes ledger directory\n5. Optionally removes log file (default: yes, unless `--keep-logs`)\n\n**Safe to call multiple times** (idempotent).\n\n---\n\n### **4. Local Playwright Config** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`)\n\n**Configuration**:\n- **Test directory**: `./e2e/local/**/*.spec.ts`\n- **Mode**: Single worker, no parallelization (`workers: 1`), no retries\n- **Timeout**: 60 seconds per test\n- **Reporter**: Simple list format\n- **Base URL**: `http://localhost:3002`\n- **Viewport**: 1280×1080 (Desktop Chrome)\n- **Tracing**: Retain on failure\n- **Web Server**:\n  - Command: `npx vite --port 3002`\n  - Reuses existing server (except in CI)\n  - Environment variables:\n    - `VITE_MOCK_MODE: \"false\"` — Use real contracts\n    - `VITE_TEST_WALLET: \"true\"` — Enable test wallet\n    - `VITE_RPC_URL: \"http://127.0.0.1:8899\"` — Localnet RPC\n    - `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK: \"localnet\"`\n\n---\n\n### **5. Root Package.json** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/package.json`)\n\n**Root-level scripts** (via Turborepo):\n- `test` — Runs all test scripts across packages\n- `test:visual` — Visual snapshot tests\n- `test:programs` — Anchor tests with bankrun (skips local validator & deploy)\n- No dedicated `test:e2e` script at root — tests are platform-specific\n\n---\n\n### **6. Base Playwright Config** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts`)\n\n**Configuration**:\n- **Test directory**: `./e2e`\n- **Mode**: Fully parallel (up to 1 worker by default)\n- **Test match**: `visual/**/*.spec.ts` (visual snapshot tests only)\n- **Base URL**: `http://localhost:3000`\n- **Web Server**:\n  - Command: `pnpm dev` (Vite dev server on port 3000)\n  - Environment: `VITE_MOCK_MODE: \"true\"` — Use mocked responses\n- **Snapshots**: Stored in `{testDir}/__snapshots__/`\n- **Visual settings**: 1.5% max diff pixel ratio\n\n---\n\n## **Execution Flow Summary**\n\n```\nLocal E2E Tests:\n  1. Run ./scripts/localnet-bootstrap.sh\n     → Starts solana-test-validator on port 8899\n     → Preloads coinflip + platform programs\n     → Writes validator PID\n\n  2. Run pnpm test:e2e:local\n     → Uses playwright.local.config.ts\n     → Starts Vite dev server on port 3002 (with real RPC)\n     → Runs tests in ./e2e/local/**/*.spec.ts\n     → Single worker, no parallelization\n\n  3. Run ./scripts/localnet-teardown.sh\n     → Stops validator\n     → Cleans up ledger & logs\n```"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a8e20499c56b727df (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 34199\ntool_uses: 6\nduration_ms: 19140</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0dadc103-b907-4a92-a199-1a6e5f8d24b0","uuid":"b7f04f9a-7a4b-4959-9c3d-ea5c41da637a","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"I need to understand the current E2E test infrastructure in the project. Please find and read these files:\n\n1. `apps/platform/package.json` — look at existing test scripts\n2. `apps/platform/scripts/localnet-bootstrap.sh` — the bootstrap script\n3. `apps/platform/scripts/localnet-teardown.sh` — the teardown script\n4. `apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts` — the local Playwright config\n5. The root `sources/rng-utopia/package.json` — look for existing test:e2e scripts\n6. `apps/platform/playwright.config.ts` — the base Playwright config\n\nReturn the full content of each file.","agentId":"a8e20499c56b727df","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've retrieved all six files. Here's a summary of the E2E test infrastructure:\n\n---\n\n## **E2E Test Infrastructure Summary**\n\n### **1. Platform App Test Scripts** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/package.json`)\n\nThree test commands are defined:\n- `test:visual` — Playwright visual snapshot tests (base config)\n- `test:visual:update` — Update visual snapshots\n- `test:real` — Real integration tests (`playwright.real.config.ts`)\n- `test:e2e:local` — Local E2E tests with localnet validator (`playwright.local.config.ts`)\n\n